{"tid":2148193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際援手　黎巴嫩當局須承諾展開獨立調查","createTime":"2020-08-09T18:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T03:24:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d31cde52b4bfbb5f4dfe05114e931f7cfe06226","tid":2148193,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T18:59:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200810/Z7QD4S2CEZUNGZFKENK2OEIYYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200810%2FZ7QD4S2CEZUNGZFKENK2OEIYYY%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=4dd8b9e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200810%2FZ7QD4S2CEZUNGZFKENK2OEIYYY%2F&h=c221d9e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200810/Z7QD4S2CEZUNGZFKENK2OEIYYY/</a><br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍和美國總統特朗普等領袖，昨日參與聯合國支持的網上峯會，討論對黎巴嫩貝魯特港口爆炸後的重建和援助事宜。<br />\n<br />\n負責主持峯會的是馬克龍，與會還包括中國、埃及、約旦、俄羅斯及沙地等國領袖都有出席，美國總統特朗普亦推文預告會出席：「人人都想幫忙！」至於與當地真主黨關係密切的伊朗，就沒有表明意願出席。馬克龍在會議開始時發言，指列強有責任支援黎巴嫩人民。「我們今日的任務是迅速、有效率地協調我們的援助，好能盡快送到黎巴嫩人手上。」他指提供援助的條件包括支持就大爆炸展開一個無黨派、可靠的獨立調查。"},{"pid":"7230431f09c0314d69f052f557b112580d4c8b7f","tid":2148193,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:11:00.000Z","msg":"調查出黎隨時又係某強國既責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7f72eaab87de5c5f43592f82f80e6d6e9ecc87","tid":2148193,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7230431f09c0314d69f052f557b112580d4c8b7f","tid":2148193,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:11:00.000Z","msg":"調查出黎隨時又係某強國既責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass